\frametitle{Improving the UI - Adding info boxes}

In the file \verb|ui.R|:

\begin{exampleblock}{}
\begin{BVerbatim}
infoBoxOutput(width = 3, "infoYears")
\end{BVerbatim}
\end{exampleblock}{}

\vspace{1em}

In the file \verb|server.R|:

\begin{exampleblock}{}
\begin{BVerbatim}
output$infoYears = renderInfoBox({
  infoBox(title,
    value = NULL,
    icon = ... ,
    color = ... ,
    fill = ...
  )
)
\end{BVerbatim}
\end{exampleblock}{}

